quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,48,"Min hollaali …ďe aaya, si wonaa haray on …ďuri adii…óo mo on mawnude. Min nanngiri …ďe lepte …óeen, mbelajo'o, …ďe nduttoto."
  43,49,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano min Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maa…óa. Pellet, ko min feewoo…ďe"."
  43,50,"Nde Min huncannoo…ďe lepte …óeen, e jaka yoo, hi…ďe pirta [ahadi]."
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yim…ďe …ďeen, o wi'i: "Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, wanaa miin jey laamu Misra? E hino …óii can…ói no ila e ley ku…ďeeji am? E on nji'ataa?"
  43,52,"Kaa mi …ďuraa teddude oo koy…óo mo e…ď…ďataa la…ď…ďinnde haala?"
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawe kaŇčŇče mbrnee e makko? Ma Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri?""
  43,54,"O …óaytini yim…ďe makko …ďen, …ďe …óowtii mo. Pellet, …ďeen …óon laatino yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe."
  43,55,"Nde …ďe tikkinnoo Min, Min yottii e ma…ď…ďe; Min njooli …ďe fof."
  43,56,"Min mba…ói …ďe ardii…ďe e yeru, wonan'de sakkiitii…ďe …ďeen."
  43,57,"Tuma nde ge…óal neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yim…ďe maa …ďeen no soo∆īira …óuum."
  43,58,"…ďe mbi'i: "Ko dewetee…ói amen …óin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko KaŇčko?" ∆Āe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wonaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko …ďe yim…ďe sa…ótu…ďe mbe√Īe."
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaani, si wanaa jiyaa…óo mo Min neemini e mum, Min mba…ói mo yeru wonan'de …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďeen."
  43,60,"Si Moen kaajuno, Min wa…ótitirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi."